  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice. Factual stub. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A cyberpunk neon colorscheme for Neovim — signature vulpes pink, teal comments, dark and light variants, and monthly color rotations. Ships with matching themes for the rest of the terminal: wezterm, kitty, ghostty, alacritty, tmux, lazygit, bat, and fzf.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The vulpes colorscheme rendering its own palette file in Neovim\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpes-nvim/editor.png\" alt=\"The vulpes colorscheme rendering its own palette file in Neovim\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/vulpes-nvim/editor.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/vulpes-nvim/editor.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/vulpes-nvim/editor.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/vulpes-nvim/editor.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The vulpes colorscheme rendering its own palette file in Neovim\" width=\"1300\" height=\"820\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.07deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1300×820\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The vulpes colorscheme rendering its own palette file in Neovim</figcaption>\n</figure>",
